'''Vuwani''' i doroba leri nga xiyenge xa Masipala wa Vhembe e xifundzheni xa [[Limpopo]] e tikweni ra [[Afrika Dzonga]].

=== Madzolonga ya ndzelekano ===
Hi lembe ra 2015, bodo ya mindzelekano ya va masipala va tiko, yi teke xiboho xo susa miganga wa Mashau na Masakona eka masipala wa Makhado, ivi yi hlanganisiwa na miganga ya [[Malamulele]], Tshikonelo, Mulenzhe, Pietboy, na Khakhanwa leyi ayiri eka masipala wa Thulamela  leswaku ku vumbiwa masipala wuntshwa.<ref>{{Cite book|url=http://www.hsrc.ac.za/uploads/pageContent/7120/VUWANI%20CASE%20STUDY%20JUNE%202016.pdf|title=Case Study on Vuwani Demarcation Protest|last=|first=|publisher=Human Sciences Research Council|year=2016|isbn=|location=|pages=3}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.observer.co.za/demarcation-board-decision-leads-to-protest-action-in-vhembe/|title=Demarcation board decision leads to protest action in Vhembe|last=Erasmus|first=Nelie|date=2015-07-23|website=Polokwane Observer|language=en-US|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2017-04-19}}</ref>

Hi lembe ra 2016, va akatiko lava ava nyamisiwile hi ku ahlula ka ka huvo ya nawu loku kondleteleke xiboho xa bodo ya va masipala, va sungule nhlungo na ku onheteriwa ka nhundzu ku hlanganisa na swikolo swa makume-nharhu endzeni ka tinhweti ta mune,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.observer.co.za/unrest-after-vuwani-demarcation-ruling/|title=Unrest after Vuwani demarcation ruling|last=Myburgh|first=RC|last2=Viljoen|first2=Barry|date=2016-05-02|website=Polokwane Observer|language=en-US|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2017-04-19|last3=Erasmus|first3=Nelie}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.capetalk.co.za/articles/13347/vuwaniprotests-an-unusual-municipal-demarcation-exercise-|title=#VuwaniProtests: an unusual municipal demarcation exercise - analyst|last=Mpondwana|first=Litha|date=2016-05-05|website=CapeTalk|language=en|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2017-04-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.702.co.za/articles/252737/27-000-pupils-blocked-from-attending-school-amid-renewed-vuwani-shutdown|title=Over 27 000 pupils blocked from attending school amid renewed Vuwani shutdown|last=Qukula|first=Qama|date=2017-04-18|website=702|language=en|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2017-04-19}}</ref> leswi kavanyeteke vukorhokeri bya mfumo na tidyondzo.<ref name=":0" />

Va aka tiko va thlele va nghenela pfhumba ro ala ku nghenelela nhlawulo wa miganga wa lembe ra 2016, laha nhlayo ya vanhu lava va hlawuleke yi chike kuya fika eka 1,600 ntsena, hambiswiritano vandla ra ANC rithlele ri hlawuriwa ku rhangela masipala wa muganga.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thenewage.co.za/4-voter-turn-out-in-vuwani/|title=4% vote in Vuwani|last=Mchunu|first=Siphiwe|date=2016-08-04|website=The New Age|language=en-GB|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2017-04-19}}</ref>

Ku onhiwa ka swi akiwo swa hulumendhe na ku kavanyetiwa ka tidyondzo swi yele e mahlweni ku fikela hi Dzivamusoko wa lembe ra 2017, nswona swi yise eku dlaweni ka vanhu vambirhi.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thenewage.co.za/police-probe-culpable-homicide-after-two-burn-to-death-in-vuwani/|title=Police probe culpable homicide after two burn to death in Vuwani|first=|date=|website=The New Age|language=en-GB|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2017-04-19}}</ref>

